<HEADLINE>
FT  09 AUG 94 / People: Time Products
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Nick Smith has been appointed md of Sekonda, and Julian Pollock md of the
Apollo Group (retail sales division), both TIME PRODUCTS subsidiaries.
</TEXT>
<XX>
Companies:-
</XX>
<CO>Sekonda.
    Apollo Group.
</CO>
<XX>
Countries:-
</XX>
<CN>GBZ  United Kingdom, EC.
</CN>
<XX>
Industries:-
</XX>
<IN>P3873 Watches, Clocks, Clockwork Operated Devices, &amp; Parts.
</IN>
<XX>
