<DATELINE>
   NEW DEHLI
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
Hyundai, the South Korean industrial group, is setting up its first joint
venture in India to make marine freight containers in collaboration with DCM
Shriram group of Delhi, writes Shiraz Sidhva in New Delhi. The new company,
DCM Hyundai, will build a wholly export-oriented unit at Polivakkam, near
